x
y
 z_y = \frac{x^2}{2} + xy + f(y) \Rightarrow z = \frac{1}{2}(x^2y+xy^2) + G(x)+F(y).
G
F
x = G(x) + F(0), \quad  y = G(0) + F(y),
G(x) = x, \ G(y) = y
